<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Logs on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/</link><description>Recent content in Logs on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>pt-BR</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>1. Introdução a Logs</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/1-introduction/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/1-introduction/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Agora você navegou diretamente de um trace de &lt;strong&gt;APM&lt;/strong&gt; para &lt;strong&gt;Logs&lt;/strong&gt; usando o link de &lt;strong&gt;Related Content&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;strong&gt;Logs&lt;/strong&gt; é a interface no-code do Splunk Observability Cloud para explorar e analisar dados de logs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A principal vantagem, assim como na integração entre &lt;strong&gt;RUM&lt;/strong&gt; e &lt;strong&gt;APM&lt;/strong&gt;, é que você está vendo seus logs no contexto das ações anteriores. Neste caso, esse contexto inclui o intervalo de tempo correspondente &lt;strong&gt;(1)&lt;/strong&gt; do trace e um filtro &lt;strong&gt;(2)&lt;/strong&gt; aplicado automaticamente ao &lt;code&gt;trace_id&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2. Filtro de Logs</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/2-log-filtering/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/2-log-filtering/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Filtrar para logs de erro&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Precisamos focar apenas nas mensagens de Error nos logs:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique no menu suspenso &lt;strong&gt;Group By&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(1)&lt;/strong&gt; e use o filtro para encontrar &lt;strong&gt;severity&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Depois de selecionar, clique no botão &lt;button class="btn-inline btn-inline--filled" type="button" style="--btn-color: #1d5d99"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt; (observe que a legenda do gráfico muda para mostrar debug, error e info).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/severity-logs.png" alt="legend" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Para selecionar apenas os logs de erro, clique na palavra error &lt;strong&gt;(2)&lt;/strong&gt; na legenda e selecione &lt;strong&gt;Add to filter&lt;/strong&gt;. Em seguida, clique em &lt;button class="btn-inline btn-inline--filled" type="button" style="--btn-color: #1d5d99"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Run Search&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt; no topo da página.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/log-observer-errors.png" alt="Error Logs" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Visualizar entradas de log</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/3-log-entry/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/pt-br/splunk4rookies/observability-cloud-short/5-logs/3-log-entry/</guid><description>&lt;section class="exercise"&gt;
&lt;header class="exercise__bar"&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/&gt;&lt;circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-label"&gt;Exercício&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-divider" aria-hidden="true"&gt;·&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="exercise__bar-title"&gt;Abrir um log de erro&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__panel"&gt;
&lt;div class="exercise__body"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clique em uma entrada de erro na tabela de logs (garanta que ela diga &lt;code&gt;hostname: &amp;quot;paymentservice-xxxx&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;, caso também apareça algum erro raro de outro serviço na lista).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Pergunta"&gt;Pergunta&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Resposta"&gt;Resposta&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Pergunta"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Com base na mensagem, o que você diria à equipe de desenvolvimento para fazer e resolver o problema?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-pt-br-splunk4rookies-observability-cloud-short-5-logs-3-log-entry-md-1-1--0-tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Resposta"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A equipe de desenvolvimento precisa reconstruir e implantar o container com um API Token válido ou fazer rollback para &lt;code&gt;v350.9&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure class="figure"&gt;
 &lt;div class="figure__inner"&gt;
 &lt;img src="../images/log-observer-log-message.png" alt="Log Message" loading="lazy" decoding="async"&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>